# CTA-PX Symbol Dictionary (v1.0)

A kid-friendly, human-friendly visual communication system.

---

## 1. Core Nodes

| Symbol | Name         | Meaning (Adult)          | Meaning (Kid) |
|--------|--------------|---------------------------|----------------|
| O      | Observer     | Human perspective/state   | Me |
| S      | Structure    | Interpretation/system     | You / The Other Person |
| R      | Relation     | Shared meaning / overlap  | Us |

---

## 2. Action Vectors

| Symbol | Meaning (Adult)           | Meaning (Kid) |
|--------|----------------------------|----------------|
| ↓      | Grounding / Stop          | Wait |
| ↑      | Request clarity            | Huh? |
| →      | Continue / forward motion | Go |
| ←      | Pull back / need space    | Space |
| ↘      | Disruption / break         | Something went wrong |
| ↖      | Recovery / re-alignment    | Fixing |

---

## 3. Deformations

| Symbol | Meaning (Adult)          | Meaning (Kid) |
|--------|---------------------------|----------------|
| ⟂      | Misalignment / confusion | I don’t get it |
| X      | Collision / blocked       | Help |
| _      | Residual wobble           | Almost ok |
| ~      | Wobble / instability      | Mixed up |
| ⊗      | Forced crossing (rail-call) | Stop + explain |

---

## 4. Flow Shapes

| Shape            | Meaning (Adult)                 | Meaning (Kid) |
|------------------|----------------------------------|----------------|
| (O→R→S)          | Smooth flow / alignment          | All good |
| (… )↘           | Flow break                       | Uh oh |
| ( )_            | Flow restored w/ wobble          | It’s ok now |
| ↺ O             | Reset                            | Do-over |
| → O             | Re-entry                         | I’m ready |

---

## 5. Combined Phrases

### Confusion
```
O ⟂ R
```

### Need space
```
O ←
```

### Request explanation
```
O ↑
```

### Need help
```
O X
```

### Reset
```
↺ O
```

### All good
```
(O→R→S)
```
